::Ramulus/Striker/Mosquitor::

Ramulus rolls out of the way as he hears a yell behind him, dodging 
Manterror's tackle and kicking out with a foot to hit the pred.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker flies backwards as missiles slam into his side, nearly rendering him 
unconscious. He gets up, the flash from Shockwave's shot causing his aim to 
be slightly off as he fires at Shockwave and the space where the missile came 
from.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor's unresponsive body flies a bit forward as Ramhorn's shots hit him, 
landing a few feet away.
